OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight with outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain affecting western hills, but
OL,8,Fregions further east likely remaining
OL,9,Flargely dry. Breezy throughout the
OL,10,Fnight and feeling mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloudy but largely dry during
OL,13,Fthe morning, before a slow-moving band
OL,14,Fof rain gradually moves eastwards
OL,15,Fduring the afternoon, fragmenting as
OL,16,Fit does so. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
